{"tid":1505571,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"現場旺角手足注意","createTime":"2019-08-25T14:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T15:10:52.000Z","uid":61417,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ced8f9fe919a3f2bedcc7f49ef138ffbb6f7f241","tid":1505571,"uid":61417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:42:39.000Z","msg":"我知道示威者係旺角集結整緊路障<br />\n唔係想阻止手足做咩<br />\n真心提醒一樣野<br />\n盡量唔好搞到去果欄附近<br />\n<br />\n以我所知之前試過有示威者<br />\n係果欄嘗試整路障<br />\n但俾果欄幾百個咕哩圍打到走左<br />\n其實果欄係九龍區同元朗一樣<br />\n三不管地帶<br />\n雖然幾乎一面倒支持政府<br />\n但成行都利字當頭<br />\n只要你唔好阻到佢做生意<br />\n果欄嘅人係完全唔會理你地出面做咩<br />\n但如果你阻到果欄做生意<br />\n佢地會比元朗嘅個班更加恐怖<br />\n每日瘋狂搬貨 個個都極高戰鬥力<br />\n真心唔想有手足再受傷<br />\n<br />\n希望可以傳達出去<br />\n<br />\nForward from Fresh_and_shoulder Fb（生果店老闆）"},{"pid":"5fc3c0c90f1ae12f61254a4d24a50655f353218e","tid":1505571,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:43:13.000Z","msg":"【置頂】828 metoo集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505524</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"921cf91946760d3a80a1ccf9b7151b0382ea061e","tid":1505571,"uid":219277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:44:06.000Z","msg":"828 metoo集會公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/withyou828\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwithyou828&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp829Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=010252a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/withyou828</a><br />\n追究黑警性暴力"},{"pid":"a5d2eccdc836b0c59bdee779094dc467d37b6852","tid":1505571,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:44:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7f34d86dd20729af8ed064f62e82e1914644d074","tid":1505571,"uid":61417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:45:11.000Z","ms